linear regression before optimization :
    a = n⋅∑(x.y)−∑(x)⋅∑(y) / n⋅∑(x**2)−∑(x)**2
    b = ∑(y)−a⋅∑(x) / n
    y = a * x + b

linear regression after optimization :
    a = a - learning_rate * ∂J/∂a
    b = b - learning_rate * ∂J/∂b
    da = ∂J/∂a = −2/n * ∑x(y − y_pred)
    db = ∂J/∂b = −2/n * ∑(y − y_pred)
    y = a * x + b